description: Lovely two-bedroom elevated first-floor condo, steps from Washington Village and proximate to W Broadway. Renovated in 2019 and 2022, a new HVAC system was installed, including central AC. This condo features beautiful chestnut floors, a recently remodeled kitchen, and two spacious bedrooms. The primary bedroom leads to a newly built deck and a rare fenced-in patio / yard, perfect for relaxing and entertaining. Highly accessible location: 10-minute walk to Andrew (MBTA) and 15-minutes to Broadway (MBTA). Come by and take a look! Open house Saturday 11:00 - 12:00 and Sunday 12:00-1:00.
